snippet.title: Void Pyramid Trailer
snippet.description:
Void Pyramid is undergoing the Steam Greenlight process. If you would like to support the game, get on Greenlight and vote it up: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782146949

This is the official trailer for the video game Void Pyramid.

Void Pyramid can be downloaded for free at www.voidpyramid.com.
